articles.title: Somerset photographer 'emotional' to be shortlisted for prize - BBC
articles.description: Josh Dury was shortlisted for this year's Astronomy Photographer of the Year competition.
articles.content:
An astrophotographer has said being shortlisted for this year's Astronomy Photographer of the Year competition was "emotional".
